<item>
            <title>[LU-19651] conf-sanity test_5h: LNetError: lnet_acceptor_remove_socket() Interface eth0 not found</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19651</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@thelustrecollective.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite runs:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/97c0c045-8320-4cad-bde8-d704478086aa&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/97c0c045-8320-4cad-bde8-d704478086aa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cc906640-ce56-44a2-b838-7447aa185016&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cc906640-ce56-44a2-b838-7447aa185016&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/gerrit-janitor/57507/testresults/conf-sanity1-ldiskfs-DNE-rocky8.10_x86_64-rocky8.10_x86_64/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/gerrit-janitor/57507/testresults/conf-sanity1-ldiskfs-DNE-rocky8.10_x86_64-rocky8.10_x86_64/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_5h failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;LNetError: 213992:0:(acceptor.c:264:lnet_acceptor_remove_socket()) Interface eth0 not found
LNetError: 14457:0:(acceptor.c:264:lnet_acceptor_remove_socket()) Interface ens2 not found
client start failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/943&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/943&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1.el9_5.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/943&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-next/943&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It appears that every test case is printing the &lt;tt&gt;lnet_acceptor_remove_socket()&lt;/tt&gt; error message on shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is happening on both Autotest and Janitor test sessions, including sessions that are passing.&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
conf-sanity test_5h - client start failed&lt;/p&gt;</description>
